{"tid":832713,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉愷威否認有新歡Britney：根本不認識她 大大大奶奶","createTime":"2018-09-23T03:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T02:04:48.000Z","uid":72009,"like":86,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"53e0a6d7d31dbb5ad648377cd8de3ea441d6a1a6","tid":832713,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:46:57.000Z","msg":"劉愷威與楊冪於2014年結婚至今，兩人因為聚少離多而屢傳婚變，但他們從未有正面回應過有關離婚的傳聞。近日網上就傳出劉愷威已經一名叫Britney的新歡，爆料者post了劉愷威與Britney的合照，聲稱是於去年10月Britney去探劉愷威班時所影的。而Britney的微博上亦有這張她與劉愷威的合照，寫住「帥帥的 #劉愷威#」。爆料者又指Britney於今年7月時透露過劉愷威跟楊冪已離婚兩年，更post了有關對話的截圖。<br />\n<br />\n對於另結新歡Britney的傳聞，劉愷威的內地工作室人員就代為回應，指劉愷威根本不認識Britney，拍這照片時他正在在拍戲，片方領導人帶了Britney到片場表示希望影合照，他只是禮貌配合對方，期間兩人並無任何交流。劉愷威方面的發言人又直斥網上傳聞不負責，指爆料者刪除了相關評論是心虛的表現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/celebrity/劉愷威否認有新歡britney-根本不認識她-080500852.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fcelebrity%2F%E5%8A%89%E6%84%B7%E5%A8%81%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%9C%89%E6%96%B0%E6%AD%A1britney-%E6%A0%B9%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8D%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%98%E5%A5%B9-080500852.html&d=3MLEuntUU0VPnla4ey6UyJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=67ff1875\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/celebrity/劉愷威否認有新歡britney-根本不認識她-080500852.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1893794/org/5b2ed8ec784cb684863cc7da32de20b7.jpg/I-muF4gcB1WjAqr2qcfY9iI_vALdCotd9CVwIfQlcCE?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1893794%2Forg%2F5b2ed8ec784cb684863cc7da32de20b7.jpg%2FI-muF4gcB1WjAqr2qcfY9iI_vALdCotd9CVwIfQlcCE%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=c0fb1222&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d2dedf0894a1059950b6d839cb542696d317688","tid":832713,"uid":72009,"like":33,"dislike":88,"score":-55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1893816/org/efa4eea05f8dc6cb1359b423133a9943.jpg/wfxO0mEZ4Wc2xko6kykTwH1e8Ept_w1rGGTO4xhkzuM?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h